    impact:["Desktop computing transformed every industry — from publishing to medicine to finance","Microsoft DOS and Windows became the dominant operating systems — making Bill Gates the world's richest person","Apple's GUI and mouse (adopted from Xerox PARC) defined the visual computing interface still used today","Home computing gave individuals the same tools as major corporations — democratizing information work"]
