    impact:["Scientific consensus: 97%+ of climate scientists agree that human activity is the primary cause","Paris Agreement (2015) — 196 nations committed to emissions reductions; NDCs still insufficient","Renewable energy revolution — solar and wind now cheapest electricity sources in history","Climate migration — 216 million internal climate migrants projected by 2050 (World Bank)","Coral reef bleaching, Amazon deforestation tipping points, permafrost methane release — tipping points increasingly documented"]
