    impact:["Israel established as a military fact — despite being outnumbered 40 million Arabs to 650,000 Jews","700,000 Palestinian refugees — the 'Nakba' whose resolution remains the core of the conflict","Israel's victory demonstrated that European military organization and motivation could overcome numerical disadvantage","Arab defeat discredited existing Arab governments — beginning decades of revolutionary upheaval in Egypt, Syria, Iraq"]
