// ── Follow State ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
let activeFollow     = null;   // current FOLLOWS entry or null
let followEvtsSorted = [];     // events in this follow, sorted by startYear
let followIdx        = 0;      // current position in followEvtsSorted

// ── Guided Story Entry Point ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
// startWWStory() — begins the WWI → WWII → Cold War guided sequence.
// Can be called from the browser console or wired to any button.
function startWWStory() {
  const thread = FOLLOWS.find(f => f.id === 'ww_story');
  if (!thread) { console.warn('ww_story thread not found'); return; }
  // Exit any current follow and clear any open connection panel first
  if (activeFollow) exitFollow();
  clearCausalLinks();
  // Enter the thread (jumps to first event, dims others, builds strip)
  enterFollow(thread);
}
// Make callable from browser console
window.startWWStory = startWWStory;

const DOT_COLOR_MAP = { WAR:'#ff4444', NAV:'#4488ff', REV:'#ff8c00', SCI:'#ffdd00', EMP:'#44ee88', DIS:'#dd44ff' };

function getFollowEventColor(evt) {
  const c = DOT_COLORS[evt.color];
  return c ? c.dot : '#aaaaff';
}

function refreshFollowStyling() {
  if (!activeFollow) {
    // Restore all to full opacity
    for (const [, layer] of activeLayers) {
      if (layer.circle) layer.circle.setStyle({ opacity: 0.7, fillOpacity: 0.11 });
      if (layer.marker) layer.marker.setOpacity(1);
    }
    return;
  }
  const followSet = new Set(activeFollow.events);
  for (const [id, layer] of activeLayers) {
    const inFollow = followSet.has(id);
    if (layer.circle) {
      layer.circle.setStyle(inFollow
        ? { opacity: 0.9, fillOpacity: 0.16, weight: 2 }
        : { opacity: 0.1, fillOpacity: 0.025, weight: 1 });
    }
    if (layer.marker) layer.marker.setOpacity(inFollow ? 1 : 0.12);
  }
}

function buildFollowPanel(query) {
  const q = (query || '').toLowerCase().trim();
  const body = document.getElementById('follow-body');
  const groups = [
    { label: 'Countries & Empires', types: ['empire','country'] },
    { label: 'Wars & Conflicts',    types: ['war'] },
    { label: 'Themes & Topics',     types: ['theme'] },
  ];
  let html = '';
  for (const grp of groups) {
    const items = FOLLOWS.filter(f =>
      grp.types.includes(f.type) &&
      (!q || f.name.toLowerCase().includes(q) || f.desc.toLowerCase().includes(q) ||
             f.type.toLowerCase().includes(q))
    );
    if (!items.length) continue;
    html += `<div class="follow-group-hdr">${grp.label}</div><div class="follow-cards">`;
    for (const f of items) {
      const cnt = f.events.filter(id => EVENTS.find(e => e.id === id)).length;
      const badgeClass = `ftb-${f.type}`;
      // Collect colors of the events for mini dots
      const dots = f.events.slice(0,8)
        .map(id => EVENTS.find(e => e.id === id))
        .filter(Boolean)
        .map(e => `<div class="follow-card-dot" style="background:${getFollowEventColor(e)}"></div>`)
        .join('');
      html += `<div class="follow-card" data-id="${f.id}">
        <div class="follow-card-top">
          <div class="follow-card-icon">${f.icon}</div>
          <div class="follow-type-badge ${badgeClass}">${f.type}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="follow-card-name">${f.name}</div>
        <div class="follow-card-desc">${f.desc}</div>
        <div class="follow-card-footer">
          <div class="follow-card-count">${cnt} events</div>
          <div class="follow-card-dots">${dots}</div>
        </div>
      </div>`;
    }
    html += '</div>';
  }
  body.innerHTML = html || '<div style="padding:20px;text-align:center;color:rgba(160,185,230,.35);font-size:12px">No threads match your search</div>';
  body.querySelectorAll('.follow-card').forEach(card => {
    card.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const f = FOLLOWS.find(x => x.id === card.dataset.id);
      if (f) enterFollow(f);
    });
  });
}

function enterFollow(f) {
  activeFollow = f;
  // Sort events in this follow by startYear
  followEvtsSorted = f.events
    .map(id => EVENTS.find(e => e.id === id))
    .filter(Boolean)
    .sort((a, b) => a.startYear - b.startYear);
  followIdx = 0;

  // Close follow overlay
  closeFollowOverlay();

  // Update follow bar
  document.getElementById('follow-bar-icon').textContent = f.icon;
  document.getElementById('follow-bar-name').textContent = f.name;
  document.getElementById('follow-bar-sub').textContent  = `${followEvtsSorted.length} events · ${followEvtsSorted[0]?.period || ''} → ${followEvtsSorted[followEvtsSorted.length-1]?.period || ''}`;
  document.getElementById('follow-bar').classList.add('visible');
  document.getElementById('follow-thread-btn').classList.add('following');
  document.getElementById('follow-thread-btn').textContent = `✓ ${f.icon} ${f.name}`;

  // Build event strip
  buildFollowStrip();
  document.getElementById('follow-event-strip').classList.add('visible');

  // Apply styling (dim other events)
  refreshFollowStyling();

  // Jump to first event
  goToFollowIdx(0);
}

function exitFollow() {
  activeFollow     = null;
  followEvtsSorted = [];
  followIdx        = 0;

  document.getElementById('follow-bar').classList.remove('visible');
  document.getElementById('follow-event-strip').classList.remove('visible');
  document.getElementById('follow-thread-btn').classList.remove('following');
  document.getElementById('follow-thread-btn').textContent = '⬡ Follow';
  closeDetailPanel();
  refreshFollowStyling();
}

function goToFollowIdx(idx) {
  if (!followEvtsSorted.length) return;
  followIdx = Math.max(0, Math.min(idx, followEvtsSorted.length - 1));
  const evt = followEvtsSorted[followIdx];

  // Advance slider to event's start year
  const yr = evt.startYear;
  playYear = yr;
  document.getElementById('timeline-slider').value = yr;
  applyYear(yr);

  // Pan map to event — offset for detail panel
  if (evt.lat && evt.lon) {
    _panForDetail(evt.lat, evt.lon, Math.max(map.getZoom(), 4));
  }

  // Open detail panel
  openDetailPanel(evt);

  // Update nav UI
  updateFollowNav();
  updateFollowStrip();

}

function updateFollowNav() {
  const counter = document.getElementById('follow-nav-counter');
  counter.textContent = `${followIdx + 1} / ${followEvtsSorted.length}`;
  document.getElementById('follow-prev-btn').disabled = followIdx === 0;
  document.getElementById('follow-next-btn').disabled = followIdx === followEvtsSorted.length - 1;
}

function buildFollowStrip() {
  const strip = document.getElementById('follow-event-strip');
  strip.innerHTML = followEvtsSorted.map((evt, i) => {
    const col = getFollowEventColor(evt);
    return `<div class="fes-item" data-idx="${i}" style="border-color:${col}22">
      <div class="fes-dot" style="background:${col}"></div>
      <span>${evt.name}</span>
    </div>`;
  }).join('');
  strip.querySelectorAll('.fes-item').forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('click', () => goToFollowIdx(Number(item.dataset.idx)));
  });
}

function updateFollowStrip() {
  document.querySelectorAll('#follow-event-strip .fes-item').forEach((item, i) => {
    item.classList.toggle('active', i === followIdx);
    if (i === followIdx) {
      item.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest', inline: 'center' });
    }
  });
}


// ── Follow overlay open/close ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
function openFollowOverlay() {
  buildFollowPanel('');
  document.getElementById('follow-overlay').classList.add('open');
  document.getElementById('follow-search').value = '';
  document.getElementById('follow-search').focus();
}
function closeFollowOverlay() {
  document.getElementById('follow-overlay').classList.remove('open');
}

// ── Follow event listeners ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
document.getElementById('follow-thread-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {
  if (activeFollow) exitFollow();
  else openFollowOverlay();
});
document.getElementById('follow-close').addEventListener('click', closeFollowOverlay);
document.getElementById('follow-overlay').addEventListener('click', e => {
  if (e.target === document.getElementById('follow-overlay')) closeFollowOverlay();
});
document.getElementById('follow-search').addEventListener('input', e => buildFollowPanel(e.target.value));
document.getElementById('follow-prev-btn').addEventListener('click', () => goToFollowIdx(followIdx - 1));
document.getElementById('follow-next-btn').addEventListener('click', () => goToFollowIdx(followIdx + 1));
document.getElementById('follow-exit-btn').addEventListener('click', exitFollow);

// Keyboard: left/right arrow to step through follow events
document.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
  if (activeFollow && !e.target.closest('input, textarea')) {
    if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') { e.preventDefault(); goToFollowIdx(followIdx + 1); }
    if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft')  { e.preventDefault(); goToFollowIdx(followIdx - 1); }
  }
  if (e.key === 'Escape') { closeFollowOverlay(); }
});

// Also refresh follow styling whenever new layers are added
const _origAddEventLayer = addEventLayer;

// ─── Historical Regions ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
map.createPane('regions');
map.getPane('regions').style.zIndex  = 202;   // above satellite (200), below borders (205)
map.getPane('regions').style.pointerEvents = 'none';

const historicalLayer = L.layerGroup().addTo(map);

